set_response_mon_understand_anything
Disk World creator help
set_response_mon_understand_anything

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_response_mon_understand_anything -  This method sets or clears the flag that allows the npc to understand any language at all.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_response_mon_understand_anything(int flag)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^flag%^RESET%^ - the new value of the flag

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/response_mon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets or clears the flag that allows the npc to understand
any language at all.  THis is useful for those times when you need an
npc that speaks/understands any language.
.EP

